---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="下载 AI Privacy Gateway — Docker / Windows / macOS"
  description="下载 AI Privacy Gateway 客户端。支持 Docker 镜像、Windows .exe、macOS .dmg。30 秒部署，保护你发给 AI 的敏感数据。"
  canonicalURL="https://privacygw.pages.dev/download">
  <Nav />

  <section class="download-section">
    <div class="container download-content">
      <h1 class="download-title">下载 Privacy Gateway</h1>
      <p class="download-description">选择适合你的版本开始保护 AI 数据隐私</p>

      <div class="download-grid">
        <!-- Docker -->
        <div class="download-card glass">
          <div class="download-icon">🐳</div>
          <h3>Docker</h3>
          <p class="download-desc">一键部署，适合服务器环境</p>
          <div class="code-block">
            <pre><code>docker-compose up -d</code></pre>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway#docker" class="btn btn-outline">查看文档</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Windows -->
        <div class="download-card glass">
          <div class="download-icon">🪟</div>
          <h3>Windows</h3>
          <p class="download-desc">便携版，双击运行</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway/releases/download/v1.0.1/PrivacyGateway.exe" class="btn btn-primary">
            下载 v1.0.1
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- macOS -->
        <div class="download-card glass">
          <div class="download-icon">🍎</div>
          <h3>macOS</h3>
          <p class="download-desc">便携版，直接运行</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway/releases/download/v1.0.1/PrivacyGateway-macos" class="btn btn-primary">
            下载 v1.0.1
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Source Code -->
        <div class="download-card glass">
          <div class="download-icon">📦</div>
          <h3>源代码</h3>
          <p class="download-desc">开源免费，欢迎贡献</p>
          <div class="code-block">
            <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway</code></pre>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway" class="btn btn-outline">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-start glass">
        <h3>快速开始</h3>
        <div class="quick-start-grid">
          <div class="quick-step">
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <h4>下载并启动</h4>
              <p>运行可执行文件或 Docker 容器</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-step">
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <h4>修改 API 地址</h4>
              <p>将 AI 客户端的 API 地址改为 <code>http://localhost:9999/v1</code></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="quick-step">
            <span class="step-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <h4>完成</h4>
              <p>敏感数据自动脱敏，无需其他配置</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="release-notes">
        <h3>v1.0.1 更新日志</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>✅ 修复：Docker 镜像构建问题（多阶段构建 Python 依赖）</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：Helm ServiceAccount 模板</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：网站网站地图 (sitemap.xml)</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：手机号、身份证、邮箱、银行卡自动脱敏</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：流式响应完美支持（SSE）</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：本地 SQLite 存储映射关系</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：自定义敏感词管理</li>
          <li>✅ 新增：可视化管理后台</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .download-section {
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
  }

  .download-content {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .download-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .download-description {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .download-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .download-card {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .download-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .download-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .download-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .code-block {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .quick-start {
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .quick-start h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quick-start-grid {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .quick-step {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .step-num {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dim));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-deep);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .quick-step h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .quick-step p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .quick-step code {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .release-notes {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .release-notes h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .release-notes ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .release-notes li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .download-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .quick-start-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .release-notes ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
